      "zh": "Mystery Ranch SATL 突击背包作为美国特种作战司令部 (SOCOM) 突击任务标配装备已服役近十年之久。现配备可拆卸式 BVS 背负系统及可调节的腰封，即使与防弹衣一同穿着时仍能实现高效的负重分配。",
      "en": "The Mystery Ranch SATL assault backpack has been the standard gear for SOCOM assault operations for nearly a decade. It now features a removable BVS system and a redirect waist belt for effective weight distribution, even when the backpack is worn over body armor."
